These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, ebony, green
1. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes green##1
2. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes mauve is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Color   | green | ebony | mauve |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, parkour, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is parkour is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | biathlon | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose, begonia
1. the person who growsrose is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
3. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Flower   | daffodil | rose | begonia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
3 different games are played: snooker, whist, monopoly
1. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Game   | snooker | monopoly | whist |

