.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, alhambra, bongani
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the ritmeester-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Cigar   | alhambra | bongani | ritmeester |

 